.about
    .about-section
        .about-logo
            img(class="logo" src="images/logo-lg.png" alt="CFxNES logo")
        .about-text
            h1
                | CFxNES (0.2.0)
            p
                | A Nintendo Entertainment System emulator written in ECMAScript 6.
            p
                | CFxNES is in early development, so many of the NES games are not playable yet.
                |  For best berformance, at least 2 GHz CPU and the #[strong latest Google Chrome]
                |  or #[strong Firefox] are recommended.
            p
                | The source code is available at #[a(href="https://github.com/jpikl/cfxnes") github]
                |  and licensed under the MIT License.
            p
                | Copyright Â© 2014-2015 Jan Pikl
            a(ng-hide="changelogVisible" href="" ng-click="showChangelog()") Show change log
            div(ng-show="changelogVisible")
                h2 Change log
                h3 0.2.0 - 2015-05-18
                h4 Fixed
                ul
                    li Emulator initialization in Internet Explorer.
                    li Build process initialization on Windows.
                    li MMC3 mapper initial state (SMB3 and Shadow of the Ninja games are now playable).
                    li Compatibility with Closure Compiler (v20150505).
                    li Compatibility with Babel compiler (v5.4.3).
                h4 Added
                ul
                    li Support for loading zipped #[code .nes] files.
                    li Visual effect when dropping files into browser window.
                    li Option to hide FPS counter.
                    li Favicon.
                h4 Changed
                ul
                    li UI optimization for small screens.
                    li js-md5 and screenfull library are optional dependencies.
                h3 0.1.0 - 2015-04-26
                ul
                    li Complete rewrite from CoffeeScript to ECMAScript 6.
